    "translation":{"eng":"…and who in this life has not associated with the devotees of Śrīmatī Rādhikā—whose moods are deep and grave and whose heart is extremely sober—how will such a person ever experience the bliss of bathing in the ocean of the rasa of ecstatic love for Śrī Śyāmasundara? Please understand this most carefully."}},{
